        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2121320042" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9012873970089563759">Usually, I hate modern poetry. I find it self-indulgent and undisciplined. This was the antithesis of that.<br/><br/>It was astounding, it was magical, it was soulful. In many ways, it was mind-blowing.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


